<style>
  .summary{
margin-top:20px;
line-height:1.8;
font-size:18px;
}

.insights{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
gap:20px;
margin-top:25px;
}

.insight-card{
background:#fafafa;
padding:20px;
border-radius:12px;
border:1px solid #eee;
}
</style>
<h1>Your Thought Insights</h1>

<div class="summary">

<p>
You’ve captured <strong><%= totalThoughts %></strong> thoughts so far.
</p>

<p>
This month you added <strong><%= thoughtsThisMonth %></strong> new reflections.
</p>

<p>
 You're on a <strong><%= streak %>-day streak</strong>.
</p>

</div>

<h2>Your Patterns</h2>

<div class="insights">

<div class="insight-card">
<h3>💡 Most Explored Theme</h3>
<p><%= mostUsedTheme %></p>
</div>

<div class="insight-card">
<h3>😊 Most Common Mood</h3>
<p><%= mostCommonMood %></p>
</div>

<div class="insight-card">
<h3>🎧 Top Learning Source</h3>
<p><%= topSource %></p>
</div>

</div>